1. Create ListView Activity with the ListView in the xml file

2. Create the card view layout in the layout res.

3. Create the model class.

4. Create the ListView adapter
       A. Make the adapter extends ArrayAdapter<ListViewModel>.
       B. implement the constructor (context,int,object).
       C. Remove the int and make the resource in the super = 0.
       D. Override getView method and inflate the card view.
       E. set the ListView and the adapter in the ListViewActivity.
